      "writtenOn": "2020-04-07T21:14:46Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Theoretically we may keep calling manageMissingBot for 180 days, in which case you never get to call manageExistingBot and reach the conversion code, but it would mean that a VM configured to live for 180 days isn\u0027t connecting for 180 days and nobody noticed or cared. In practice such a situation \"probably\" isn\u0027t occurring, but we have no way to know so we should probably handle it by calling convertToBinary in manageBot instead of in manageExistingBot. This is slightly less efficient because it will convert entities that are about to be deleted anyway, but it\u0027s not a big deal.",
      "revId": "d5b4e71b86bccaa262255d41e4901c121fd08bca",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
